column4: <content>1 zw/w foto [Notitie in onbekend handschrift]: Pieter Bruegel. Landscape with a Hermit. Collection Dr. GHA Clowes, Indianapolis, Indiana; [Notitie FG]: The painting of the rocks and of the tree looks later, cf. rocks in Jan Brueghel's Temptation of St. Anthony, Vienna. Could this be a Jan Brueghel after some earlier work?</content>
